id: The Try Guys Answer the Web's Most Searched Questions
paragraph:
Subscribe to 'WIRED'
                  on YouTube to keep up with all of
                  our latest videos and shows.
                Keith, Ned, Zach, and Eugene of The Try Guys take the WIRED Autocomplete Interview and answer the internet's most searched questions about The Try Guys and themselves. Are The Try Guys still at BuzzFeed? Are they all really friends? Do they all live in LA? The Try Guys answer all these questions and more!© 2018 Condé Nast. All rights reserved.
